Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We continue to offer funeral songs to the ones selected out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the Undertakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will resist GHQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who rules this country as though they own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against everyone and everything that attempts to select us out.
