Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I think you all know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but GHQ has declared a Level 2 state of emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in connection with yesterday's incident in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you have info on these terrorists who call themselves the Undertakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're supposed to report it to the authorities immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class has a new transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yuzuriha Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I've seen her from somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Egoist?! There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Kusama Kanon. I'm the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ask me if you have any questions, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I wouldn't join the Undertakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do you have all your books and things already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so why did she come to my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you're missing any, I'll go borrow them from the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have P.E. today, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I-Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... So, what do you think about the Undertakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you randomly ask something like that, Souta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Egoist's songs seem kind of Undertaker-ish, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought maybe she liked them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so, what are the other Egoist members like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting Yuzuriha on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. This guy's name is Tamadate Souta, and he's a huge fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So forgive him for being rude, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I'm Samukawa Yahiro, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Yahiro and Shu over there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,formed this club called the Contemporary Visual Culture Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was wondering... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, man, chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be in the same class for the rest of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just take it slow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I just know that her coming here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}must have something to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, when you see Inori in person, she's kinda like a doll, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, she looks more like CG in real life, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that, Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori is {\i1}not{\i0} CG! Open your eyes, moron!{You just called her a doll, you cunt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you {\i1}ever{\i0} say that to her face, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori's sensitive and easily hurt, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He called me a moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why doesn't anybody think about how my feelings can get hurt?{what a fucking pussy}{ikr}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There I go being selfish again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I'll just try not to get involved with her anymore!{inb4 she's living there}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inori?!{called it}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are all these boxes?{every fucking cliche}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you at my apartment?! And why can you open the door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funell did it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I really can't be rude right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Keido, how will you take responsibility for what happened in Roppongi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be putting Major Segai in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of all Undertaker-related matters from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Segai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with the Norma Gene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a genetic drug that's been in vogue lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right, Dr. Ouma?{shu's mom?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. It was an incidental discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the development of the Apocalypse Virus vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I assigned him to figure out its distribution channels,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gave me a whole picture of the industry within a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's sharp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost too sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we give him worthy prey, he'll hunt it with all his energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hang it up to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, that was a work e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. "To talk, or not to talk, that is the question," I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's roll him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I explain it to Mom when she gets home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Haruka. Senior Researcher at Sephirah Genomics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only comes home about once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlikely to be back here for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've done a whole background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu, am I a burden to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... you're not a {\i1}burden{\i0}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know why you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, sorry to come so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is that movie we were talking about. Wanna watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thanks... You came all the way here for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting weird today. I thought so, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question... I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message came. Come with me, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err, there's a really good explanation for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if anything happens, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Samukawa Yahiro your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really looks after the people around him, and he can be sympathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally different from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any friends, Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does a person have to have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just finished. The OAU is very interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me a condition, though. I'll report in more detail later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like a wanted criminal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change the world just by running around with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, anyone tailing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what are you planning by sending Inori to my school and apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone witnessed us during the battle yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this person were from the fort, I could have taken care of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems it's an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A student from your school.{inb4 it's the guy who wanted to watch the movie}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my school? Why would...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Norma Gene. Have you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it's some drug that's really popular these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy was there to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the deal, this person was called "Sugar".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that's probably an alias, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance you and Inori were seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? How many students do you think go to my school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to find one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw out the Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, you can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell what people's Voids are, can't you, Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you couldn't have made that plan in Roppongi if you hadn't known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's convenient how quickly you figure things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. I can see Voids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in that battle, I sensed the presence of the witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that witness's Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the Temporary Disaster Law currently in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,terrorists have no human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the witness identifies you, you won't escape harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've informed Inori of the Void's shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your peaceful everyday life, protect it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you memorized the Void rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Voids can only be drawn from people seventeen years old or younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is unclear. Or else it's a secret from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, when you withdraw a Void from someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that person loses their memories of the time surrounding the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's from the shock of the intron memory field being released, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that works in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, right now I need to experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hare will forgive me even if I screw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Shu? If you'd just said something, I would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Ouma Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeosansLight\bord0\c&H535746&\b1\pos(568,706)\frx0\fry0\frz11.127\blur1\fad(200,200)}Scum!!!!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeosansLight\bord0\c&H535746&\b1\frx0\fry0\blur1\fad(200,0)\fs45\frz12.339\pos(753,276)}He needs to get that sex drive under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeosansLight\bord0\c&H535746&\b1\frx0\fry0\blur1\fad(200,0)\pos(477,618)\frz12.52}What a total creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I was on track to get through three years of school without standing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe everyone could do me a favor, and just forget about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I screw it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's necessary when you're drawing out a Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get nervous when I make eye contact with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I lose my grip on the conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm looking into your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking in between your eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai told me the important thing is for them to think you made eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring someone down this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I kinda figured it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've got the hang of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you watch. Now, this starts for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm sor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so what Void am I supposed to be looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. You'll understand when you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}are{\i0} Voids? Why do they come in so many forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Void's form and function
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reflect things like the person's fears or complexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say it's the shape of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voids are... the shape of their hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rough! I've done nothing but run around since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but if you'd joined the Undertakers, they'd have put you through worse.{BRILLIANT COMMENT, BRO}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The class rep will probably cool down after a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's apologize to her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but will she actually forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might just cut me into pieces with a pair of shears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you talking about that movie from last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking. Your tastes are kind of unusual, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did {\i1}that{\i0} come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that's a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to say appearances can be deceiving sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I {\i1}was{\i0} seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're judging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I mean, knowing you, you must have had your reasons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna keep pretending to be friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all over from the moment you called me "Sugar"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't pretend that everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because guys like {\i1}you{\i0} just {\i1}assume{\i0} I'm harmless
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I have to keep acting that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep pretending to be someone I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all {\i1}your{\i0} fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yahiro's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai said he succumbed to temptation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he'll be a threat to us if we don't eliminate him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to forget the persona{PERSONA} Yahiro worked so hard to build!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to just assume it was all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So put that down, Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, when Yahiro woke up, we made a promise to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We promised he wouldn't tell anyone about the Undertakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I wouldn't tell anyone about the Norma Gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like it was the first time Yahiro and I really met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report from Inori! "Witness problem solved. Steer clear from now on."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them do what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu... can I stay with you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know you. And the others. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think you can do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GHQ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives, Yahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are under arrest.
